==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Everliving
<hw>Ev`er*liv"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Living always; immoral; eternal; <as>as, the <ex>everliving</ex>
God</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Continual; incessant; unintermitted.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Evermore</ent>⟦br⟧
